title: #48- Wildcat & BasicallyIDoWrk Reveal Secret Vanoss Project & MrBeast Challenge
itunes:title: #48- Wildcat & BasicallyIDoWrk Reveal Secret Vanoss Project & MrBeast Challenge
description: Wildcat, aka Tyler Wine, and BasicallyIDoWrk, aka Marcel Cunningham, return to the CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast for the second time! On this episode, they cover a multitude of exciting events in their current lives, moments in gaming, and more. One of their recent joint endeavors is an upcoming animated series called Alpha Betas, which also features their long-time collaborators, VanossGaming & Terroriser.
